sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP (plaintext)
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant LLM as vLLM / LLM Inference

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>{"model": "...", "messages": [...]}
        Note over Gateway: Inject route-specific detector<br/>config into payload
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert<br/>{"detectors": {...}, "model": "...", ...}
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input detection<br/>(content filtering)
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>LLM: Chat completion request
        LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Output detection<br/>(response filtering)
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with<br/>detection metadata
        alt Detections found + fallback configured
            Note over Gateway: Replace response choices<br/>with fallback_message
            Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(fallback message)
        else No detections or no fallback
            Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original orchestrator response)
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion (SSE)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>{"stream": true, "model": "...", ...}
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>{"stream": true, ...}<br/>Optional mTLS
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input detection
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>LLM: Streaming chat completion
        loop SSE chunks
            LLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE chunk
            Orchestrator->>Detectors: Per-chunk detection
            Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection result
            Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE event with<br/>detection metadata
            alt Detection in chunk + fallback
                Note over Gateway: Replace chunk content<br/>with fallback, set<br/>finish_reason="stop"
                Gateway-->>Client: SSE event (fallback)
            else No detection
                Gateway-->>Client: SSE event (pass-through)
            end
        end
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE: [DONE]
    end
